<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-18 02:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4921 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HKN-KINGS-SENATORS-RE     03-18 0525
