<P>
   INDONESIA-TIMOR (Hong Kong) _ A week after the United Nations
announced a plan for East Timor to vote on autonomy from Indonesia,
a leading East Timorese advocate said here today that the ballot
should not be held until Indonesia withdraws some troops from the
strife-torn island. By Mark Landler.
