believed was related to Algerian IOC member Mohamed Zerguini. Turns
out, he is the grandson of the late Hadj Mohammed Benjoullen of
Morocco, who died two years ago. Scally's uncle is Atlanta
restarateur Rafih Benjelloun, who had plenty of contacts with
Olympic people but said Scally did not. (Fish, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 40.
