<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-18 17:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5575 &Cx1f; ttg-z
a l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SWARTZ-COLUMN-$ADV25-     03-18 0840
