<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    CONDITIONS IN NURSING HOMES MAY BE WORSENING
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (a) general news categories
 &HT;    By JULIA MALONE
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ A quarter of the nation's nursing homes have severe
