   &QL; 
 &QL; 
COYOTES-REAX (Phoenix) - Talk of an offer to buy the Phoenix
Coyotes is part of a plot to keep them in Phoenix and sink an
effort to build the team a new arena in south Scottsdale. That was
the reaction Thursday of Scottsdale Mayor Sam Campana and other
arena supporters a day after revelations in the Arizona Republic
that an entertainment group wants to buy the team and keep them at
America West Arena. But other cities who mighht team up with
Scottsdale to create a stadium district to help fund the $140
million arena, say the possibility of a sale doesn't affect them.
