AMWEST (Washington) - It is an emotionally charged standoff between
entrenched opponents _ flight attendants vs. America West _ with
both sides fighting for the upper hand in the last hours of
negotiations before Friday night's strike deadline. By PETER
CORBETT. Story will move in the ``F'' category. &QL;
