<P>
   NY-DIALLO-PROTESTS (New York) _ Protesters of the shooting here
by police of an unarmed West African immigrant have adopted an
event-a-day strategy. They have also put an emphasis on celebrity
rather than just numbers, as in the recent arrests and handcuffing
of Rep. Charles B. Rangel and former Mayor David Dinkins. By Dan
Barry.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
