<SLUG> BC-BKC-MARYLAND-STJOHNS19-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Red Storm blows away Terps
 &HT;    By Jack Wilkinson
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   KNOXVILLE, Tenn. _ Now Maryland knows how Indiana suffered. Five
