 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    WRAPIDO, WRAPIDO. Mexican food giants Gruma and Grupo Industrial
Bimbo are leading the charge into a lucrative tortilla market ...
in the United States.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-TORTILLA-INVASION-LATINTRADE-NYTSF.
